{"type":"message","id":"eaae30c2","parentId":"4acc9d80","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:35:01.202Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:investment-research-data-source-health-0935 09:35来福投研会-数据源健康巡检] 执行以下任务：\n1. 进入 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\n2. 运行 python3 scripts/run_investment_research_data_source_health_probe.py --scope intraday\n3. 运行 python3 scripts/generate_investment_research_data_source_health_broadcast.py --scope intraday\n4. 读取 health probe json 和 health broadcast md\n5. 如果状态是 healthy 或 offhours_guarded，则回复 NO_REPLY\n6. 如果状态是 watch_guarded 或 degraded，则用中文简短汇报：状态、采样标的、最大价差分歧、触发项、broadcast 路径、probe 路径\n7. 若状态为 degraded，明确写出建议立即临时会商\nCurrent time: Friday, April 3rd, 2026 — 9:35 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-03 01:35 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775180101185}}
